5年开创性记录，并选择他们最大的热门歌曲。</p><p>在户外活动中的支持将来自特别嘉宾<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/friendly-fires">友好的大火</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-hives">蜂箱</a>（英国独家表演），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mysterines">谜团</a>和康妮·康斯坦斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/connie-constance">（Connie Constance）</a> 。</p><p>门票将于本周五（12月8日）GMT上午10点进行一般销售 - <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbloc-party-tickets%2Fartist%2F953414" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里购买</a>。另外，预定的预定将于明天（12月7日）同时上线。 </p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad1 id_ad_content-horiz-center"><div class="apester-media apester-unit" data-manual-top-desktop="64" data-manual-top-mobile="55" data-token="5644b81019aec6d348309b65" data-context="true" data-tags="" data-fallback="true"><div id="apester-companion-placement-above-70687285-db26-43b2-bfda-d6433b208c10" class="apester-companion-above-container"><div id="apester-companion-video-above" class="companion container-video"><div id="apester-companion-video-above-70687285-db26-43b2-bfda-d6433b208c10" class="apester-ad-container"><div id="apester-companion-video-above-70687285-db26-43b2-bfda-d6433b208c10gui"><div id="av-container" class=" av-desktop hide-controls"><div id="av-inner"><div id="slot"><div id="videoslot" class="loaded"><p>备受赞誉的唱片后来获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">汞奖</a>提名，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/2005-2-1045347">在2005年被评为<em>NME</em>的年度专辑</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0gegIitKhv/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="b